lead_paragraph: Celtic have been fined 10,000 euros (£8,633.11) by Europe's governing body UEFA over Palestinian flags displayed by fans during their Champions League match against Hapoel Beer Sheva last month.

headline.print_headline: Celtic Fined by UEFA Over Supporters' Palestinian Flags
